```plantuml
@startuml oovk_dataengg-covid19-aws
left to right direction
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #f8f9fa
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "User"

package "AWS" {
  rectangle "S3\nData Lake" as S3 #e0f7fa
  rectangle "Athena\nQuery Service" as Athena #e0f7fa
  rectangle "Redshift\nData Warehouse" as Redshift #e0f7fa
}

rectangle "Jupyter Notebook\n(covid19_project.ipynb)" as Notebook #ffffff
rectangle "Pandas DataFrames" as Pandas #f0f4c3
rectangle "Dimensional Model\n(factCovid, dimRegion\n, dimHospital, dimDate)" as DimModel #dcedc8

User --> Notebook : Initiates ETL

Notebook --> S3 : Extracts Raw Data
S3 --> Athena : Executes Queries

Athena --> Notebook : Returns DataFrames
Notebook --> Pandas : Transforms Data

Pandas --> DimModel : Builds Dimensional Model
DimModel --> Notebook : Prepares CSVs

Notebook --> S3 : Stores Transformed Data (CSV)
Notebook --> Redshift : Loads Data into Warehouse

@enduml
```